{"tid":1566430,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港人依家只係sheeps 而無sheepdogs","createTime":"2019-09-13T14:43:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T17:03:01.000Z","uid":38448,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a85401da520c10e93d8d6d1ad8663c2a50ea78a8","tid":1566430,"uid":38448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:43:39.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;wolves, sheep, and sheepdogs&rdquo;<br />\n如果大家有睇過american sniper 應該都會有印象<br />\n<br />\n呢個說話既原著係出自Lieutenant Colonel David Grossman既書On Combat<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;If you have no capacity for violence then you are a healthy productive citizen: a sheep. <br />\n<br />\nIf you have a capacity for violence and no empathy for your fellow citizens, then you have defined an aggressive sociopath&mdash;a wolf. <br />\n<br />\nBut what if you have a capacity for violence, and a deep love for your fellow citizens? Then you are a sheepdog, a warrior, someone who is walking the hero&rsquo;s path&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n放諸近期既藍絲暴力事件 不難睇出<br />\n其實香港人太多只係綿羊仔 甚至乎保護自己都做唔到<br />\n被人打完 淨係覺得嬲 但完全唔會諗以武制暴<br />\n即使係10對1 20對1<br />\n更甚既係走去報警 相信敵人既爪牙會幫你 <br />\n天真到可憐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隨著破窗效應 對住我地既暴力只會無日無之<br />\n直到佢地付出代價為止<br />\n<br />\n其實已經好多巴打講過好多次<br />\n但情況依然照舊<br />\n包括今日女手足跳閘 俾人搶野<br />\n從結果嚟睇 報左警 女手足俾人罰500 廢老咩事都無<br />\n<br />\n下一次廢老又會再嚟到 反正咩事都無"},{"pid":"5a09b183d811db0e6b457220f8c1c68aed14b225","tid":1566430,"uid":38448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:49:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e1d28ffb26f765433a06c9ea5ce44926f5c62406","tid":1566430,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:56:35.000Z","msg":"Sheepdogs = 間間茶餐廳部部長開播住ＴＶＢ既電視機<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a80539a87bfbba1a98eee00d064f18fdc5bc754",